MetaLocator,is,a,feature,rich,mapping,and,locator,service,that,can,be,used,to,add,and,manage,searchable,maps,on,a,website,It,can,serve,as,any,type,of,location,directory,such,as,a,store,locator,ATM,locator,or,vendor,list,MetaLocator,is,lightweight,portable,highly,configurable,and,works,in,any,language,Users,can,add,MetaLocator,maps,their,websites,by,copying,and,pasting,a,line,of,JavaScript,code,onto,the,site,The,map,appears,as,a,seamless,aspect,of,the,site,with,no,branding,or,ads,Developers,can,interact,with,MetaLocator,com,using,an,XML,RPC,API,in,order,to,add,delete,update,publish,and,unpublish,stored,locations